  <brief_title>The Pleiotropic Effects of Atorvastatin When Combined With Common Antihypertenisve Medications.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Pleiotropic Effects of Atorvastatin When Combined With Common Antihypertenisve Medications: A Comparison of Amlodipine and Hydrochlorothiazide</official_title>
