  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effects of the cholesterol medication taken with
      each blood pressure medication alone on heart disease risk factors including blood pressure,
      cholesterol, inflammation, blood sugar control, blood vessal function, and other heart
      disease risk factors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
